				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$C_{A} = C_{C} \frac{{\eta (1 + \eta )^{k - 1} }}{{\left( {1 + \eta } \right)^{k} - 1}} + C_{O}$$\end{document}where CA and k are the annuity and designed lifetime of the considered PtG plant, respectively; η denotes the interest rate.

